snippet.title: The Morgue: Hospital Escape (Indie Horror Game Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
A horror game inspired by the Texas chainsaw massacre and puppet combo games.

EDIT: The game will not be submitted to the Scream Jam 2020 anymore. The game will have a longer development period and maintenance support.

Download for PC:
https://solodevinteractive.itch.io/the-morgue

Download for Android: (please leave 5⭐ star and comment please.. thanks for the support)
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.SoloDevInteractive.TheMorgueHospitalEscape

Early Access:
https://www.patreon.com/posts/42344838

My personal website:
https://pinoygamedev.wordpress.com/

Facebook developer page:
https://www.facebook.com/solodevinteractive/

Twitter developer page:
https://twitter.com/solodevi

Unlock behind the scenes and exclusive posts. Also if you wanted your name to be included in my videos as a special thanks.
https://www.patreon.com/solodevinteractive

Music Attribution:
Sound effects by TunePocket – Unlimited royalty free music and sound effects for video creators
